channel.title: The gods
channel.description:
Video: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C4Etqb3jMgo&feature=related
VID2 : http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k1_au635bPU&feature=related
NOTE* old video's ^^ dont want to give out much / and it is a on and off project in this video it only shows combat.
Okay so im not posting MUCH information and No pictures, because i dont want anything to be seen yet!
so basiclly, i come to moparscape because i think that new users would give me there best opinion upon my new genration runescape private server..
what im saying is.. i need testers.
but its not that simple. i need trusted users.
because my project has never ever been created or tested before.
What my project consits of: NOTHING ABOUT RUNESCAPE NOTHING ABOUT RSPS BUT BASED AROUND GODS.
once you log on * a new interface will pop up basically like character create but its more complex you will have the choices becoming one of the gods of the heavens and hells, consiting of zeus, hades, hercules, and etc.
Each one has its own individual powers and has its own reponsibilities, like protecting their city in the heavens and fighting off evil.
custom items that are out of this world, and animations and gfx's.
and once you log in, you will auto matically have the feelings of fantasy and imgination.
my goals for this project is to bring something new to the table.. this project took me almost 4 months to complete, now i just need testers to give me there opinions.
being a tester does not give you any advantage once the server is released, you will not become a admin you will not become a mod or anything..THIS SERVER IS BASE AROUND FATASY AND THE POWER OF IMGINATION.
i hope you guys really appreciate what ive been working on.
p.s for thoughs of you who love pking/ im sorry to disappoint you but there is no pking, theres not even a wildy, these are areas that you have never seen before..but there is lots of gore/ blood and etc.
There are some requirements to becoming a tester and there is only 1: must be able to play runescape in hd and fullscreen.
you have to download my client / it will come with an installer for easy installation and the download s only 13 secs long.
- Dell.
